  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You became a hermit-like living style, and consequently, with a great deal of depression on the family members.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In this case, my mother and I lived alone, which was in a very nice street, which we were forced to vacate because the apartment house was owned by Gentiles.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The force to move came, of course, in 1938, with the Crystal Night, or the Night of Crystal, Kristallnacht, which happened on the 9th of November, at which date, you know, all hell broke loose all over Germany.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I realize the Germans always claim that it was coincidental, but in every major city, it was a fully organized and planned signal that from now on, you know, persecution of the Jews will have to be to a most dramatic and not yet final solution, but dramatic end.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very much so.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You don't forget these things from first of all, purely visual point of view.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We lived on a street, where as it is very common in Europe, that you have large apartment houses, where you live above the first floor, the ground floor, the ground floor being mostly stores.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We have areas in the United States that are very similar, especially San Francisco.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There are whole districts where you have small stores, small businesses.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Maybe you might call them, in those days, mom and pop stores, and you lived above that.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That's a very common European architectural style.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "When you live in such a street, in such an area, and you hear incredible noises, which means the shattering of glass, looting, yelling, screaming, and most important of all, the order of fires, of smoke, when stores and business were set aflame, and of course, all the synagogues.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We happened to have lived in a fairly close proximity to the major synagogue.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
